hjb.jms
Class MetadataReaderAssistant

java.lang.Object
  hjb.jms.MetadataReaderAssistant
public class MetadataReaderAssistant
extends Object

MetadataReaderAssistant is to used translate values that are attributes of the JMS ConnectionMetaData to encoded HJB form.

Author:
Tim Emiola
